{"tid":751030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話通州街橋底雜既人其實有無諗過好多人好慘？","createTime":"2018-07-21T13:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T05:35:18.000Z","uid":102240,"like":12,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d08eb777d5e52cbee4223fc2d09686736f4219","tid":751030,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:15:57.000Z","msg":"你係咪真係有去了解過嗰度啲露宿者先?中學嗰陣我有去做過一啲探訪見到好多時都真係一啲唔夠收入去租屋嘅人，一係就仔女唔理，好多都有唔經歷。露宿者中有道友的確係事實。<br />\n但有一班得唔到幫助嘅人，只係靠一啲義工或者類似明哥嗰啲餐廳嘅幫忙同微簿嘅收入去維生。其實政府已經無好好面對露宿者嘅問題，可以有安穩生活嘅我地幫唔幫忙都好，或者至少可以做嘅係唔好覺得佢哋係渣滓，唔係人。老實吖嗰啲地方有幾何其他人會特別去行或者用，倒不如留番一丁點嘅空間畀佢哋生存啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53b0fb8ed5105e8f86d9cc4f46604fc09bca0b4","tid":751030,"uid":47359,"like":14,"dislike":8,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:22:25.000Z","msg":"樓主五毛咩咩妹<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/212223_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F212223_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b2c8a49a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fca309f03bce30f60ba0eaba60451bcbff9400da","tid":751030,"uid":33566,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:22:32.000Z","msg":"將佢地擺去你屋企樓下點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NIMBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNIMBY&d=b%2FGaIoTPJVadsgKuDjk%2FfNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=20e9ef9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NIMBY</a>"},{"pid":"0c984d190bc9b5e6426bf9a31f96a199ab904ce5","tid":751030,"uid":56147,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"有諗過   但只要係人地慘 唔係自己慘<br />\n就諗下算<br />\n尤其經濟上廢, 直頭要憎要恥笑先岩<br />\n<br />\n相信呢個先係香港主流價值"},{"pid":"81485573ad2fe014fbb83a2590e2a8cd7e79b7e0","tid":751030,"uid":102240,"like":1,"dislike